在以色列，反英情绪根植于英国在历史上[[巴勒斯坦托管地|巴勒斯坦托管地]]的统治和政策；在现代则根植于英国媒体反以色列的立场。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.jewishmag.com/106mag/euroarabia/euroarabia.htm |title=Why are the Brits so anti-Israel? |publisher=Jewishmag.com |date= |accessdate=2010-06-01 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100507210623/http://www.jewishmag.com/106mag/euroarabia/euroarabia.htm |archivedate=2010-05-07 |deadurl=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |last=Rosenblum |first=Jonathan |url=http://www.aish.com/jw/s/48898202.html |title=UK Anti- Semitism |publisher=Aish.com |date=2005-06-04 |accessdate=2010-06-01 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100606214655/http://www.aish.com/jw/s/48898202.html |archivedate=2010-06-06 |deadurl=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |last=Liphshiz |first=Cnaan |url=http://www.haaretz.com/hasen/spages/1102548.html |title=Watchdog: British anti-Semitism doubled after Gaza war |work=Israel News |publisher=Haaretz |date= |accessdate=2010-06-01 |archive-date=2009-11-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20091103061819/http://www.haaretz.com/hasen/spages/1102548.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.ynetnews.com/articles/0,7340,L-3257290,00.html |title=British anti-Semitism |work=Israel Opinion |publisher=Ynetnews.com |date=1995-06-20 |accessdate=2010-06-01 |archive-date=2019-05-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190517194707/https://www.ynetnews.com/articles/0,7340,L-3257290,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

根据2009年上半年在英国境内609起反犹太人的事件，<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.haaretz.com/hasen/spages/1102548.html |title=Watchdog: British anti-Semitism doubled after Gaza war - Haaretz - Israel News |accessdate=2014-07-22 |archive-date=2009-11-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20091103061819/http://www.haaretz.com/hasen/spages/1102548.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>以及众多英国组织抵制以色列的宣言，<ref name="ynetnews.com">{{Cite web |url=http://www.ynetnews.com/articles/0,7340,L-3257290,00.html |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2014-07-22 |archive-date=2019-05-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190517194707/https://www.ynetnews.com/articles/0,7340,L-3257290,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>一些以色列人声称英国是反以色列和[[反犹太主义|反犹太主义]]的。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.jewishmag.com/106mag/euroarabia/euroarabia.htm |title=Why are the Brits so anti-Israel? |accessdate=2014-07-22 |archive-date=2010-05-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100507210623/http://www.jewishmag.com/106mag/euroarabia/euroarabia.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.aish.com/jw/s/48898202.html |title=UK Anti- Semitism |accessdate=2014-07-22 |archive-date=2010-06-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100606214655/http://www.aish.com/jw/s/48898202.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>据埃坦·吉尔伯称，“英国媒体系统性地支持巴勒斯坦人，并公开其对以色列带有偏见的政策报告。左翼报纸[[卫报|卫报]]和[[独立报|独立报]]定期发表指责、反以色列的社论，并且其在以色列的记者寄给报社带有偏见，有时甚至是虚假、错误的报导。著名的[[英国广播公司|英国广播公司]]则长期以来作为巴勒斯坦宣传的传声筒。”<ref name="ynetnews.com"/>在2010年，前任右翼团体“强国教授”主席罗恩·布雷曼在以色列的主流报纸之一的[[国土报|国土报]]上声称英国已经扶植并为以色列在约旦阿拉伯区域的敌人进行武装。他将英国媒体描述为反以色列的并称英国“荣光已逝”。<ref name="haaretz1">{{Cite web |url=http://www.haaretz.com/hasen/spages/1153375.html |title=End British obsession with anti-Israel propaganda - Haaretz - Israel News |accessdate=2014-07-22 |archive-date=2010-04-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100418181051/http://www.haaretz.com/hasen/spages/1153375.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>他同时指責英国控制[[苏格兰|苏格兰]]、[[威尔士|威尔士]]和[[北爱尔兰|北爱尔兰]]，<ref name="haaretz1"/>并接着声称英国占领了[[爱尔兰岛|爱尔兰岛]]。<ref name="haaretz1"/>他还声